languages.text: "Зачем блюстители явились, Лорд-капитана охранять? Неужто думают, что мы {mf|его|ее} в обиду дадим?!"
"Why are there enforcers here? To guard the Lord Captain? Do they think we'd do something to harm {mf|His Lordship|Her Ladyship}?"

languages.text: «¿Por qué hay guardias aquí? ¿Para proteger {mf|al|a la} Lord Capitán? ¿Es que se creen que íbamos a hacerle daño?».
languages.original_text: "Why are there enforcers here? To guard the Lord Captain? Do they think we'd do something to harm {mf|His Lordship|Her Ladyship}?"

traits.locale_text: «¿Por qué hay guardias aquí? ¿Para proteger {mf|al|a la} Lord Capitán? ¿Es que se creen que íbamos a hacerle daño?».

languages.text: 「なぜエンフォーサー達がここにいるのですか？ロード・キャプテンを警護するため？私たちが陛下に危害を加えるとでも思っているのでしょうか？」
languages.original_text: "Why are there enforcers here? To guard the Lord Captain? Do they think we'd do something to harm {mf|His Lordship|Her Ladyship}?"

traits.locale_text: 「なぜエンフォーサー達がここにいるのですか？ロード・キャプテンを警護するため？私たちが陛下に危害を加えるとでも思っているのでしょうか？」

languages.text: “这种地方怎么会有执法者？是为了保护舰长大人吗？莫非他们以为我们打算伤害大人吗？”
languages.original_text: "Why are there enforcers here? To guard the Lord Captain? Do they think we'd do something to harm {mf|His Lordship|Her Ladyship}?"

traits.locale_text: “这种地方怎么会有执法者？是为了保护舰长大人吗？莫非他们以为我们打算伤害大人吗？”

languages.text: "Warum sind die Enforcer hier? Bewachen sie den Lord Captain? Denken sie, wir würden {mf|Seiner Lordschaft|Ihrer Ladyschaft} etwas antun?"
languages.original_text: "Why are there enforcers here? To guard the Lord Captain? Do they think we'd do something to harm {mf|His Lordship|Her Ladyship}?"

traits.locale_text: "Warum sind die Enforcer hier? Bewachen sie den Lord Captain? Denken sie, wir würden {mf|Seiner Lordschaft|Ihrer Ladyschaft} etwas antun?"

languages.text: « Qu'est-ce que les prévôts font là ? Ils protègent {mf|le seigneur-capitaine|la seigneure-capitaine} ? Ils croient vraiment qu'on ferait du mal à Sa Seigneurie ? »
languages.original_text: "Why are there enforcers here? To guard the Lord Captain? Do they think we'd do something to harm {mf|His Lordship|Her Ladyship}?"

languages.text: "Burada neden infazcılar var? Lord Kaptan'ı korumak için mi? {mf|Lord|Leydi} Hazretleri'ne zarar verecek bir şey yapacağımızı mı düşünüyorsunuz?"
